  "title": "Sales Engineer (West / 5 Days Work) - SS10",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Engineer</strong></p><ul><li>Working Hours: 8.15am - 5.30pm</li><li>Working Days: 5 Days [Monday - Friday]</li><li>Location: Gul Crescent / Joo Koon, Singapore</li><li>Salary: $3000 - $4000 + $70 Phone Allowance + 14 Days AL</li><li>Entitled to $1020 (transport allowance) + AWS + Yearly Commission </li></ul><p>Summary: Sales Engineer role in the Water Jetting & Industrial Cleaning division under the Sales Department, preferable exposure from petrochemical, oil refinery, shipyard, oil & gas industries.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Polytechnic Diploma or equivalent; preferably in a business associated or engineering related field</li><li>Experienced in corporate / industrial sales, especially in the oil and gas , petrochemical, oil refinery, shipyard settings.</li><li>Holding a Class 3 driving license and own a car</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Serve existing assigned accounts and prospect potential new customers</li><li>Learn & familiarize our products well, understand users’ needs, and so be able to offer solutions and assistance to meet their requirements</li><li>Perform hands-on product demonstrations, as well as occasionally conduct presentations to mid-size audiences including management levels</li></ul><p>Samuel Siaw</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd</p><p>EA No: 14C7279</p><p>Reg No: R2412474</p><p></p>",
